# sqlx migration checksums hash the raw bytes of each migration file.
# Line endings MUST be stable (LF) across every OS/checkout, otherwise the
# tauri-plugin-sql integrity check panics at startup on Windows (CRLF) when the
# DB recorded an LF checksum. Keep SQL — and DB migrations specifically — as LF.
*.sql text eol=lf
src-tauri/src/db/migrations/*.sql text eol=lf
